國人咩心態</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實韓國人好鍾意90年代或之前既香港電影/音樂!</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係?</blockquote><br />\n係<br />\n甜蜜蜜<br />\n張國榮電影<br />\n發哥電影<br />\n天若有情<br />\n王家衛電影<br />\n英雄本色 佢地直頭當係神 好似話年年新年電視都會重播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有成龍韓國人上一代個啲無人唔識佢<br />\n連rm都請成龍上去<br />\n間中背景音樂會有張國榮既當年情<br />\n連電視劇都有一幕係個背景有一大幅張國榮海報同埋個演員係度扮張國榮套唔知咩戲既舞步<br />\n今時今日既香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n阿飛正傳舞  JUNGLE DRUM.<br />\n幾時到我地彈返起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想港產片彈返起呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39bd85a4944ef1becf192663551a098782a2fb82","tid":269194,"uid":59687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T21:14:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇過片話哥哥喺英雄本色後喺韓國紅到痴哂線<br />\n成龍8/90年代喺日本又係痴哂線 食勁多㗎妹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家輪流轉 香港啲𡃁妹迷kpop <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sl2s_ASu9vw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dsl2s_ASu9vw&d=UmI0bGDlw8nB3PvrRXnxYMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=b36b5239\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sl2s_ASu9vw</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xYUKZc2oT5w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxYUKZc2oT5w&d=UmI0bGDlw8nB3PvrRXnxYMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=3c89276a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xYUKZc2oT5w</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor